Bliss,after a long,long week
Sweet dreams to salve the wounds mind accrues

Title: Abyss, The
description: Is the dream the inspiration or the inspiration the dream? Do your lyrics come from your heart or are they hidden in your soul?
text:
#vssnature

I stare
into the #abyss
wondering
if this truly is
a entry into hell
or just the last kiss
of a lost star
searching for home
